Provision of registry keeping services on a decentralized basis at the customer's preferred branch;
Minimum package of required document;
Efficient use of time;
Competitive tariffs;
Comprehensive support for registry keeping and custody-related issues;
Fast, courteous and quality service by specialized staff.
The companies that will sign a Registry Maintenance Agreement with the Bank within the period from February 1 to April 30, 2021 will be served free of charge for one month and, moreover, will be twice provided with a FREE reference on the list of registered owners.

