With a view of getting children to love nature, ARARATBANK announces a painting and photography contest Green Armenia for children aged 5-16 years. To join the contest, it is necessary to:
send a thematic painting or photo via private message by the 20th of June, 2019.
share the post to the Facebook page of the Bank.
like the official Facebook page of ARARATBANK.
The contest will have two WINNERS – one painter and one photographer, who will be selected based on the most liked photo or painting and will enjoy a one-day vacation for 4 persons in ARARAT RESORT rest house in Tsaghkadzor.  Two winners more — 1 painter and 1 photographer — will receive themed surprise gifts, whose works will be selected by ARARATBANK management committee based on voting. Winners will be also issued the certificates of participation. 
Contest deadline – 25.06.2019;
The names of the winners will be published on 27.06.2019;
Gift-giving ceremony will be held on 01.07.2019.
Below are the main preconditions for participation in the contest:
The painting/photo sent from fake pages will not be considered;
Only one painting/photo may be sent;
The painting/photo which does not correspond to the theme will not be considered;
Paintings/photos will be published on the Facebook page within 2 working days once they are sent;
Fake likes will not be considered when summing up the results of the contest;
Paintings/photos of the contest may be sent also from the parents’ pages.
ARARATBANK regularly holds similar contests on its Facebook page with a view of developing drawing skills of children and their ability to see the beauty.
Should you have any contest-related questions, you are free to call at 010 59 23 23 available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week or write us through official Facebook page of the Bank.

